    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_7306670504350749925.png",
                "id": "talent16844",
                "key": "Cooling Treatment",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Cooling Treatment"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Memberikan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Bitey Shark</span> kepada diri sendiri, memasuki <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span>, dan mendapatkan 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">\"poin Nightsoul\"</span>. (Setelah Karakter memasuki <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span>, Skill ini tidak dapat digunakan) </p><p>(Karakter yang memiliki Bitey Shark dapat menggunakan Skill: <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Sharky Surfboard</span>)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p>Karakter yang terpengaruh dapat mengakumulasi \"poin Nightsoul\". (Maksimum 2 poin)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/6eca0515aa0b943ce4863f23e7bac54f_89332415098890119.png",
                "id": "talent12662",
                "key": "Surfshark Wavebreaker",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Surfshark Wavebreaker"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span> dan memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shark Missile</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/de980cad3d9422986776632fa61c2eff_3642788311504263938.png",
                "id": "talent22979",
                "key": "Boomsharka-laka",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Boomsharka-laka"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Kartu Equipment</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Setelah kedua pemain bertukar Karakter dan saat Mualani menjadi Karakter Aktif:</span> mengonsumsi 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">\"poin Nightsoul\"</span> akan memberikan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Bite Target</span> kepada Karakter aktif lawan.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Teknik</span>: Sharky Surfboard </p><p>Ketika <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">poin Nightsoul</span> Karakter yang terpengaruh mencapai 0, kartu ini akan dibuang. Saat kartu ini dibuang, Karakter yang terpengaruh mengakhiri <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7428673736714487068.png",
                "id": "talent59074",
                "key": "Bitey Shark",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/6fc92bf55b26c115eefe4f2a113677e0_4749659397659399463.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Bitey Shark"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Teknik</span></p><p>Berganti ke Karaktermu yang sebelumnya dan memberikan 1 lapis <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Bite Target</span> kepada Karakter aktif lawan. (Jika semua Karakter standby-mu sudah gugur, akan mengonsumsi 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">poin Nightsoul</span> tambahan)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7655555352909910963.png",
                "id": "talent77374",
                "key": "Sharky Surfboard",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Sharky Surfboard"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span> (Dapat ditumpuk tanpa batas)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1252297400834980964.png",
                "id": "talent74585",
                "key": "Shark Missile",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/f2ea88f3013a7c33fb47942114373377_4430349720295796101.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Shark Missile"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Hydro dan memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan sebuah [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] yang memberikan +2 poin DMG untuk kasus Pyro/Electro DMG-mu selanjutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_6166187627079585265.png",
                "id": "talent4335",
                "key": "Hydro DMG Bonus",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Hydro DMG Bonus"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Bite Target</span></strong></p><p>Saat menerima DMG dari Mualani atau Shark Missile:</p><p>efek ini akan dihapus dan setiap lapisnya akan mengakibatkan DMG +2.</p><p>(Jumlah lapisan dapat ditumpuk tanpa batas)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/08/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_653842439793037898.png",
